Visit your local branch today
*st.george stamething
stgeorge.com.au/maxisaver
Fees, charges apply. Read T&Cs at stgeorge.com.au before making a decision and consider if the product is right for you. The 1.90% p.a.fixed bonusrate is only available for the first three months from account opening if you
open a new Maxi Saver account and have not held a Maxi Saver account before. Personal customers only. To hold a Maxi Saver account, you must also hold an eligible St.George transaction or savings account in the same name.
Fees & charges may be payable on the other account 2017 St.George Bank -A Division of Westpac Banking Corporation ABN 33007 457 141 AFSL and Australian credit licence 233714.
